title: RT - Daily news: WikiLeaks to brief press after release of CIA vault (Livestream)
text:
WikiLeaks to brief press after release of CIA vault (Livestream) Published time: 7 Mar, 2017 16:28 Get short URL © Axel Schmidt / Reuters WikiLeaks has published a cache of confidential CIA documents, exposing a massive hacking program in the agency’s cyber espionage effort. Tags WikiLeaks 
The release came ahead of schedule on Tuesday after the group claimed that its planned press conference fell victim to a cyberattack.
